<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦١٢٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7060">أَبُو التَّيَّاحِ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسَ بْنَ مَالِكٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«إِنْ كَانَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> لَيُخَالِطُنَا حَتَّى يَقُولَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لِأَخٍ لِي صَغِيرٍ يَا أَبَا عُمَيْرٍ، مَا فَعَلَ النُّغَيْرُ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>